t":"8-bit"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ quantized 的 TensorFlow Lite 模型，而且模型还必须先用 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"edgetpu_compiler"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 编译成 Edge TPU 可执行版本。运行时侧不管用 Python 还是 C/C++，都需要 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"libedgetpu"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 和对应的 TensorFlow Lite 库。这说明它不是“通用 NPU 后端”，而是 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"TFLite + compiler + runtime + 设备"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 的产品化闭环。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-yk9igy1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-yk9igy1","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这也解释了它为什么更像“端侧部署工具链”而不是通用编译框架。官方示例里，未被 Edge TPU 吃下的部分可以继续留在 CPU，所以平台价值在于把高收益主路径固化，而不是承诺所有层都能透明上 NPU。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-8mmu881","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-8mmu881","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这类平台的关键启发是："}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-5lakkn3","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-5lakkn3","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-ml9lv8n","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-ml9lv8n","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-f2c0aw0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-f2c0aw0","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"NPU 不只是一个核，而是完整产品"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-mymiso7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-mymiso7","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-asrr9cn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-asrr9cn","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"电源、接口、外设和工具链会直接影响可用性"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-snjpjty","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-snjpjty","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-m0dvz26","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-m0dvz26","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"边缘部署场景里，“拿到板子能跑起来”本身就是重要价值"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-eyrazql","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-eyrazql","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"所以 Edge TPU 代表的不是“最强架构”，而是“从硬件到开发体验的端侧产品化闭环”。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-s6nks3z","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-s6nks3z","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5. 软件栈主导路线：OpenVINO NPU 插件"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-a2x94ee","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-a2x94ee","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"OpenVINO 案例最值得看的地方不在 NPU 核心本体，而在软件栈组织方式："}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-khrojoy","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-khrojoy","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-6h110lu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-6h110lu","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-qqo5qar","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-qqo5qar","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"插件架构"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-eeuq6g3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-eeuq6g3","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-xfp6xk3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-xfp6xk3","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"模型优化器"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-cbngekx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-cbngekx","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-y0gbgrs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-y0gbgrs","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"异步执行引擎"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-2mexyn0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-2mexyn0","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-jtnsia2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-jtnsia2","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"与 CPU/GPU/iGPU/NPU 多插件协同"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-fas5seh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-fas5seh","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"OpenVINO 官方 NPU 文档把这条路线也钉得很实：用户入口是 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"compile_model(..., \"NPU\")"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，随后由 plugin / driver / compiler 把 IR 编成设备工件；如果开启 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"ov::cache_dir"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，后续请求可以直接 import 已缓存模型，而不是每次重新编译。与此同时，当前 NPU 路径仍强调 static-shape 支持，offline blob import 只建议开发用途。也就是说，它确实是“软件栈主导路线”，但不是没有平台边界，而是把这些边界收进统一 API 和插件体系里。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-vqwxgs7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-vqwxgs7","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"它说明了一件很关键的事："}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-7vzmtcb","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-7vzmtcb","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-t6govgd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-t6govgd","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101902-vbj1qg3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101902-vbj1qg3","updated":"20260424101902"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对很多平台来说，用户真正接触到的不是 NPU 寄存器和命令流"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101902-1gxoumv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"2026042